getValueLabel.description: A function to get the accessible label text representing the current value in a human-readable format. If not provided, the value label will be read as the numeric value as a percentage of the max value.
getValueLabel.description_zh: 一个函数，用于获取以人类可读格式表示当前值的可访问标签文本。如果未提供，则值标签将读取为数值，以最大值的百分比表示。

as.description: The element or component this component should render as. Can be overwrite by asChild
as.description_zh: 此组件应呈现为的元素或组件。可以被 asChild 覆盖

asChild.description: Change the default rendered element for the one passed as a child, merging their props and behavior.
asChild.description_zh: 更改作为子元素传递的默认渲染元素，合并其道具和行为。
